- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper deals with abstract syntax trees and generating valid JavaScript tests.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses neural network language models to guide the fuzzer.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also relevant as the paper uses machine learning techniques to improve the effectiveness of the fuzzer.
